Package: notecase
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Hierarchical text notes manager
 NoteCase is a hierarchical text notes manager (outliner).
 It helps you organize your everyday text notes into a single document
 with individual notes placed into a tree-like structure.
 To ensure your privacy an encrypted document format is supported along
 with a standard unencrypted one.
